extendedInfo.description: Unmatched in education, attendees call this the best meeting in ophthalmology! This year's ASCRS Symposium on Cataract, IOL and Refractive Surgery, ASOA Congress on Ophthalmic Practice Management, and Technicians and Nurses Program offer the best educational programs to keep you on top of the latest in ophthalmic surgery and practice. ASCRS and ASOA give you the tools you need to stay in the forefront of your profession.
